    <title>BOOST_TEST_DONT_PRINT_LOG_VALUE usage</title>
    
    <simpara>
     Try to comment out BOOST_TEST_DONT_PRINT_LOG_VALUE statement and you end up with compile time error.
    </simpara>
   </btl-example>
